*jsrvis, a cli llm client

	usage: jarvis [-h] [-f FILE_NAME] [-w WORD] [-p PROVIDER] [-m MODEL] [-c COMMAND]

	options:
	-h, --help            show this help message and exit
	-f FILE_NAME, --file_name FILE_NAME
                        send a file to llm
	-w WORD, --word WORD  ask llm a question
	-p PROVIDER, --provider PROVIDER
                        change the provider
	-m MODEL, --model MODEL
                        change a model
	-c COMMAND, --command COMMAND
                        let llm gennerate commands